269. Memorandum of ConversationSource: Library of Congress, Manuscript Division, Kissinger Papers, TS 26, Geopolitical
                        Files, France, Chronological File, 19 July–20 Dec 1973. Top Secret;
                        Sensitive; Eyes Only. The meeting took place at the Elysée Palace. Kissinger also met with Jobert December 19. (Ibid.)
